## ID Naming by Category

### 1. Forms & Form Elements

#### Form Containers

```html
<!-- Authentication forms -->
<form id="user-login-form">
<form id="user-signup-form">
<form id="user-password-reset-form">

<!-- Resource forms -->
<form id="article-create-form">
<form id="article-edit-form">
<form id="comment-reply-form">
<form id="profile-update-form">

<!-- Search forms -->
<form id="article-search-form">
<form id="global-search-form">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[action]-form`

#### Input Fields

```html
<!-- Text inputs -->
<input id="user-email-input" type="email">
<input id="user-password-input" type="password">
<input id="user-password-confirmation-input" type="password">
<input id="article-title-input" type="text">
<input id="article-slug-input" type="text">
<input id="search-query-input" type="search">

<!-- Number inputs -->
<input id="article-views-count-input" type="number">
<input id="product-price-input" type="number">

<!-- Date inputs -->
<input id="article-published-date-input" type="date">
<input id="user-birth-date-input" type="date">

<!-- Hidden inputs -->
<input id="article-id-hidden-input" type="hidden">
<input id="csrf-token-hidden-input" type="hidden">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[field]-input` or `[resource]-[field]-[type]-input`

#### Textareas

```html
<textarea id="article-body-textarea"></textarea>
<textarea id="comment-content-textarea"></textarea>
<textarea id="message-body-textarea"></textarea>
<textarea id="feedback-text-textarea"></textarea>
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[field]-textarea`

#### Select Dropdowns

```html
<select id="article-status-select">
<select id="article-category-select">
<select id="user-role-select">
<select id="country-select">
<select id="language-select">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[field]-select`

#### Checkboxes

```html
<!-- Single checkboxes -->
<input id="article-published-checkbox" type="checkbox">
<input id="user-terms-accepted-checkbox" type="checkbox">
<input id="comment-notify-replies-checkbox" type="checkbox">
<input id="user-newsletter-subscribed-checkbox" type="checkbox">

<!-- Checkbox groups (add value to ID) -->
<input id="article-tags-technology-checkbox" type="checkbox" value="technology">
<input id="article-tags-tutorial-checkbox" type="checkbox" value="tutorial">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[field]-checkbox` or `[resource]-[field]-[value]-checkbox`

#### Radio Buttons

```html
<!-- Radio groups (always include value in ID) -->
<input id="article-visibility-public-radio" type="radio" name="visibility" value="public">
<input id="article-visibility-private-radio" type="radio" name="visibility" value="private">
<input id="article-visibility-unlisted-radio" type="radio" name="visibility" value="unlisted">

<!-- Payment methods -->
<input id="payment-method-card-radio" type="radio" name="payment_method" value="card">
<input id="payment-method-paypal-radio" type="radio" name="payment_method" value="paypal">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[field]-[value]-radio`

#### Buttons

```html
<!-- Submit buttons -->
<button id="user-login-submit-button" type="submit">
<button id="article-save-button" type="submit">
<button id="comment-post-button" type="submit">

<!-- Action buttons (non-submit) -->
<button id="article-preview-button" type="button">
<button id="save-draft-button" type="button">
<button id="cancel-edit-button" type="button">
<button id="delete-confirm-button" type="button">
<button id="modal-close-button" type="button">

<!-- Icon buttons (with descriptive action) -->
<button id="comment-edit-button" type="button">
<button id="comment-delete-button" type="button">
<button id="article-share-button" type="button">
```

**Pattern:** `[resource]-[action]-button` or `[action]-button`

#### Labels

```html
<!-- Labels must match input IDs with "for" attribute -->
<label for="user-email-input">Email Address</label>
<input id="user-email-input" type="email">

<label for="article-title-input">Article Title</label>
<input id="article-title-input" type="text">

<label for="article-category-select">Category</label>
<select id="article-category-select">
```

**Rule:** Label `for` attribute MUST match input `id` exactly

