### 2. Navigation Elements

#### Main Navigation

```html
<nav id="main-navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
  <ul id="main-nav-list">
    <li id="nav-home-item">
      <a id="nav-home-link" href="/">Home</a>
    </li>
    <li id="nav-articles-item">
      <a id="nav-articles-link" href="/articles">Articles</a>
    </li>
    <li id="nav-about-item">
      <a id="nav-about-link" href="/about">About</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</nav>
```

#### Mobile Navigation

```html
<nav id="mobile-navigation">
  <button id="mobile-menu-toggle-button" aria-expanded="false">
    <span>Menu</span>
  </button>
  <div id="mobile-menu-overlay" class="hidden">
    <div id="mobile-menu-content">
      <ul id="mobile-nav-list">
        <li><a id="mobile-nav-home-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>
```

#### User Account Menu

```html
<nav id="user-account-menu">
  <button id="user-menu-toggle-button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
    Account
  </button>
  <div id="user-menu-dropdown" class="hidden">
    <a id="user-profile-link" href="/profile">Profile</a>
    <a id="user-settings-link" href="/settings">Settings</a>
    <a id="user-notifications-link" href="/notifications">Notifications</a>
    <button id="user-logout-button" type="button">Logout</button>
  </div>
</nav>
```

#### Breadcrumb Navigation

```html
<nav id="breadcrumb-navigation" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <ol id="breadcrumb-list">
    <li><a id="breadcrumb-home-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a id="breadcrumb-articles-link" href="/articles">Articles</a></li>
    <li><span id="breadcrumb-current-page">Current Article</span></li>
  </ol>
</nav>
```

#### Pagination

```html
<nav id="pagination-navigation" aria-label="Pagination">
  <a id="pagination-first-link" href="?page=1">First</a>
  <a id="pagination-previous-link" href="?page=2">Previous</a>
  <span id="pagination-current-page">Page 3</span>
  <a id="pagination-next-link" href="?page=4">Next</a>
  <a id="pagination-last-link" href="?page=10">Last</a>
</nav>
```

#### Sidebar Navigation

```html
<nav id="sidebar-navigation">
  <h2 id="sidebar-nav-heading">Categories</h2>
  <ul id="sidebar-nav-list">
    <li><a id="sidebar-nav-technology-link" href="/categories/technology">Technology</a></li>
    <li><a id="sidebar-nav-tutorials-link" href="/categories/tutorials">Tutorials</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>
```

**Navigation Patterns:**
- Main nav container: `main-navigation`
- Mobile nav: `mobile-navigation`
- User menus: `user-account-menu`, `user-menu-dropdown`
- Nav links: `nav-[page]-link` or `[context]-nav-[page]-link`
- Nav items: `nav-[page]-item`
- Toggle buttons: `[menu]-toggle-button`

